			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="Speak to Ceres Olsin - S_GLO_IronThrone_Group1_Prisoner2 ced0a558-b5ed-4493-a499-1890ec48fbfb - (-58; 37; 71)  in the Dock warehouse after saving them.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Quick setup:&#xD;&#xA;- Load CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use Debug Book (Ctrl + Shift + 9)&#xD;&#xA;- Set Quest Flags and Options -&gt; Act3 (LOW) -&gt; Iron Throne -&gt; Change State -&gt; Back At Docks -&gt; MajoritySaved&#xD;&#xA;- Then talk to the NPC" />
